items.name: Spa and Wellness Club
items.description: Dedicated to promoting wellness and relaxation, the Spa and Wellness Club organizes retreats like 'VE!!'â€”an immersive spa retreat in nature designed to rejuvenate body and mind.

items.name: Leadership Development Association
items.description: Focusing on developing future leaders through interactive activities, this association holds events such as the 'Site Leader Training' which combines karaoke and fun with serious leadership training.

items.name: GEM Retreat Center
items.description: Organizes retreats aimed at personal and professional growth, such as the 'GEM Kick off Retreat' held at Stony Acres Retreat Center, offering participants leadership skills and personal development.

items.name: CSO Staff Retreat Group
items.description: Specializes in creating bonding and recharging experiences for community service staff, organizing retreats like the 'CSO Staff Retreat' in secret locations to enhance team spirit and cohesion.

items.name: Lehigh Leadership Program
items.description: Opens applications for transformative leadership experiences and provides training and resources as seen in the 'Leadership Lehigh Applications' event.

items.name: Lehigh Office of Student Leadership
items.description: Hosts application processes for leadership programs, providing students with opportunities to apply for roles in initiatives such as the 'Leadership Lehigh Application'.

items.name: UP Comedy Club
items.description: Brings entertainment to campus with events like 'UP Thursday Night Comedy featuring Steve Hofstetter', offering a night of laughter and relaxation for students and staff.

items.name: Lehigh Sorority Recruitment Board
items.description: Coordinates recruitment events across campus, such as the 'Sorority Recruitment - 1st Rho Gamma Hall Meetings', aimed at introducing new students to sorority life.
